com.basho.riak.client.builders
Class DomainBucketBuilder<T>

java.lang.Object
  com.basho.riak.client.builders.DomainBucketBuilder<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the DomainBucket to be built
public class DomainBucketBuilder<T>
extends Object

For creating a DomainBucket

Defaults are as follows:

  • ConflictResolver : DefaultResolver
  • Converter : JSONConverter
  • Retrier : DefaultRetrier.attempts(int) configured for 3 attempts
  • MutationProducer : anonymous instance that produces a ClobberMutation for MutationProducer.produce(Object)

    russell
